# RUNME

To run the program interactively you can use the following command:

```shell
deno run --allow-read --allow-write --allow-env --allow-net ./main.ts
```

To run the program directly from the CLI you can use this command with arguements:

```shell
deno run --allow-read --allow-write --allow-env --allow-net ./main.ts --file <file-path>
```

For specific files to use for the CLI arguement you can look at the sample inputs in the Project pdf or look at ./src/test/examples.